  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK242">
<l>nallāṟṟā ṉāṭiyaruḷāḷka pallāṟṟāṟ</l>
<l>ṟēriṉu maḵtē tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(Stand) in the good path, consider, and be kind. Even considering according to the conflicting tenets of the different sects, kindness will be your best aid, (in the acquisition of heavenly bliss.)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
